  <entry>
    <title>Web日记</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2023/03/25/2023.03.25/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2023/03/25/2023.03.25/</id>
    <published>2023-03-25T09:14:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-04-16T12:42:01.212Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="03-25"><a href="#03-25" class="headerlink" title="03.25"></a>03.25</h1><p><strong>小学了一下Markdown的语法</strong></p><p>开始写网站的第一部分啦，每天都在这更新一下进度</p><p>基本命令</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean 清楚缓存区</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo g 生成静态文件</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo server 在本地查看网页</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo d 部署到云端网页上</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>hexo生成新页面</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page xxx(如link)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改了人物头像 添加了外站链接</p><h1 id="04-11"><a href="#04-11" class="headerlink" title="04.11"></a>04.11</h1><p>打开字数统计：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-wordcount --save</span><br><span class="line">修改wordcount配置：</span><br><span class="line">wordcount:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  post_wordcount: true</span><br><span class="line">  min2read: true</span><br><span class="line">  total_wordcount: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Beautify (美化主题页面)</span><br><span class="line">beautify:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  field: post # site/post</span><br><span class="line">  title-prefix-icon: &#x27;\f0c1&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">  title-prefix-icon-color: &#x27;#6495ED&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>全局字体配置</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">font:</span><br><span class="line">  global-font-size:</span><br><span class="line">  code-font-size:</span><br><span class="line">  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Lato, Roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif</span><br><span class="line">  code-font-family: consolas, Menlo, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改主页文字及效果</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># the subtitle on homepage (主頁subtitle)</span><br><span class="line">subtitle:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  # Typewriter Effect (打字效果)</span><br><span class="line">  effect: true</span><br><span class="line">  # Customize typed.js (配置typed.js)</span><br><span class="line">  # https://github.com/mattboldt/typed.js/#customization</span><br><span class="line">  typed_option:</span><br><span class="line">  # source 調用第三方服務</span><br><span class="line">  # source: false 關閉調用</span><br><span class="line">  # source: 1  調用一言網的一句話（簡體） https://hitokoto.cn/</span><br><span class="line">  # source: 2  調用一句網（簡體） https://yijuzhan.com/</span><br><span class="line">  # source: 3  調用今日詩詞（簡體） https://www.jinrishici.com/</span><br><span class="line">  # subtitle 會先顯示 source , 再顯示 sub 的內容</span><br><span class="line">  source: false</span><br><span class="line">  # 如果關閉打字效果，subtitle 只會顯示 sub 的第一行文字</span><br><span class="line">  sub:</span><br><span class="line">    - 少年人总想看世间山海,可又偏偏不会等待</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>主页加载动画</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Loading Animation (主页加载动画)</span><br><span class="line">preloader:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  # source</span><br><span class="line">  # 1. fullpage-loading</span><br><span class="line">  # 2. pace (progress bar)</span><br><span class="line">  source: 1</span><br><span class="line">  # pace theme (see https://codebyzach.github.io/pace/)</span><br><span class="line">  pace_css_url:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="04-12"><a href="#04-12" class="headerlink" title="04.12"></a>04.12</h1><p>改变背景图片，默认为白色</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">background：</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>1点击显示大图<br>2显示在中间（动画）</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">fancybox:true</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>点击复制会显示弹窗</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Snackbar (Toast Notification 彈窗)</span><br><span class="line"># https://github.com/polonel/SnackBar</span><br><span class="line"># position 彈窗位置</span><br><span class="line"># 可選 top-left / top-center / top-right / bottom-left / bottom-center / bottom-right</span><br><span class="line">snackbar:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: false</span><br><span class="line">  position: bottom-left</span><br><span class="line">  bg_light: &#x27;#49b1f5&#x27; # The background color of Toast Notification in light mode</span><br><span class="line">  bg_dark: &#x27;#1f1f1f&#x27; # The background color of Toast Notification in dark mode</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 04.13</span><br><span class="line">完成了音乐播放器的设置（aplayer）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>npm install –save hexo-tag-aplayer<br>在_config.yml文件下添加</p><p>aplayer:<br>meting: true<br>asset_inject: false<br>开启主题配置中的aplayerInject<br>aplayerInject:<br> enable: true<br> per_page: true</p><p>播放器设置<br>全局播放<br>打开pjax<br>pjax:<br>enable: ture<br>exclude:</p></blockquote><p>~~~</p><h1 id="04-16"><a href="#04-16" class="headerlink" title="04.16"></a>04.16</h1><p>修改了github -》 csdn链接</p><h1 id="已知问题："><a href="#已知问题：" class="headerlink" title="已知问题："></a>已知问题：</h1><blockquote><p>无法播放收费音乐<br>播放器样式太丑</p><p>进度条未导入（preloader:）</p><p>背景图片无法更改</p></blockquote><h1 id="优化："><a href="#优化：" class="headerlink" title="优化："></a>优化：</h1><blockquote><p>标签页<br>分类<br>评论<br>文章节选<br>文章图片</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
